headline: Mark J. Barrenechea Appointed to SentinelOne Board of Directors
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., December 03, 2025--SentinelOne (NYSE: S), the leader in AI-native cybersecurity, today announced the appointment of Mark J. Barrenechea to its board of directors.
